    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six unassessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The hemolysis bench validation (vr-hemolysis-bench-2026q1) was conducted under the rc2 solver build; the assessment team reviewed the CFX-2026Q1-0047 change-log entry and concluded the single-patch difference between rc2 and the released build (ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7) is limited to residual-log formatting and does not affect simulation outputs. On this basis the validation evidence is considered applicable to the model of record and the COU is accepted at Medium assurance level.",
